<div class="helpText">
	<h3>To use Springer Link eBooks:</h3>
	<a target='_blank' href='{$path}/files/econtent_help/springerlink.pdf'><img src="{$path}/images/pdficon_small.png" alt="Printable Help"/> Printable Version</a>
	<ol>
		<li>Search the library's catalog for Springer Link eBooks you want to read.</li>
		<li>Click the <b>Access EBook</b> button for the book.</li>
		<li>You will be prompted for your name and library barcode for access to the SpringerLink website.</li>
		<li>You will be redirected to the Springer Link site after you are authenticated.</li>
		<li>Select the <b>Sign up / Log in</b> link in the upper right corner.</li>
		<li>Create an account by entering your First Name, Last Name, and email.   You will also need to select a password for the site.</li>

	</ol>
</div>
